# 8. 一緒に猛特訓！

Minori: One, two, three, four...
Minori: And pose! How do I look?!
Miku: <Oh, really cute!>
Miku: <But you lost balance there for a split second, so try to stay on axis when you go to pose...!>
Minori: Yeah, you're right! Airi even told me just the other day that my core still needs a lot of work...
Minori: So, Miku, let me try that again!
Miku: <Okay! I don't mind watching...>
Miku: <But you've been at it for close to an hour and a half now. Why don't you take a quick break first...?>
Minori: Whoa, you're right! I completely lost track of time!
Minori: Hmm... I was hoping that you'd watch me practice interacting with an audience afterwards...
Miku: <Did something happen recently, Minori...?>
Minori: Huh?
Miku: <You have a really good work ethic, but it seems odd for you to be trying this hard...>
Minori: Oh...
Minori: So... It has to do with something that happened during our last TV shoot...
Miku: <TV shoot...? Oh, do you mean for Mr. Arimura's show?>
Minori: Yeah. You watched it, right, Miku?
Audience Member A: So, where'd the original guests go? Why is MORE MORE JUMP! or whoever here instead?
Audience Member B: But I still wish LiLia were here.
Minori: After I overheard what those audience members were saying, even though I knew that we couldn't make up for not being LiLia, I decided that I was going to make sure they got to have fun.
Minori: But I also feel that I could've done more for them during the first half of our shoot. If only I'd realized sooner...
Miku: <Minori...>
Minori: Which is why, even though I still have a lot to learn, I want to become a fully-fledged idol as fast as I can.
Miku: <I see... That's really admirable, Minori.>
Miku: <So, I'll be more than happy to help you!>
Minori: Wait, really?!
Miku: <Yes! While we're at it, why don't we train together in SEKAI once we're done taking our break?>
Miku: <I'm sure it would be better if you practiced imagining talking to an audience while on a real stage.>
Minori: Oh, you're right! That'd definitely feel more like the real thing!
Minori: Then, I'll head over now!
Minori: Phew! I made it through!
Minori: That was a good practice...! Plenty of dancing and interacting with an audience! I feel a lot more confident now! Thanks, Miku!
Miku: Hehe. You feel more confident because you put in the work, Minori!
Miku: You even came up with some nice ideas for making things fun. I hope you get a chance to use them during your next shoot...!
Minori: Me too! I can't wait for our next one♪
Minori: Still, I have to ask...
Minori: Don't things seem a little too quiet around here today?
Miku: Oh, come to think of it, I haven't seen anyone else here since we began practicing. We were at it for quite a while too.
Minori: Where do you think everyone's gone?
Miku: Hmm... MEIKO and KAITO said they were going over to see Haruka, but they should be back by now...
Miku: Huh?
Minori: What's wrong?
Miku: That path over there... I don't think I've ever seen it before...
Minori: What path?
Minori: H-Hey, you're right... I've never seen this before either.
Minori: Do you think the others are wherever this path leads to?
Miku: What...?
Miku: Then, let's see where it takes us.
Minori: O-Okay. I'm a little scared... But, I also kinda want to know where it goes...
Minori: For now, let's go take a quick look!
Minori: Th-Th-Th...
Minori: There's a new area?!
Miku: Wow...! Oh, that looks like a stage way over on the other side, doesn't it?
Miku: Also, this vast field of flowers is so beautiful.
Miku: Minori? Is something wrong?
Minori: I thought I just saw a shadowy figure just now. Of a little girl...
Miku: What...?!
Miku: B-But I don't see anything... Maybe it was something else?
Minori: M-Maybe. But given where we are, what else could it have been...?
Minori: I think she ran this way...
???: Hmm... What do I do...?
Miku: Huh...
Flower's Emitted Voice: Alright... Again...! One, two...
Minori: That voice... Is it coming from this flower...?
Miku: I think so. But why...?
Flower's Emitted Voice: No, I still can't get it right... If only...I could...be more like...
Minori: Hmm... I'm having trouble making out what it's saying...
Minori: I'll try moving a little closer and...
Miku: Huh...?!
Minori's Voice: Wah!! S-So bright!!!
Miku: M-Minori?!
